import React from 'react'
import { Card, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function Issues () {
  return (
    <Container className="issues-container">
      <Row>
        <Container>
          <Card>
            <Card.Body>This is some text within a card body.</Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Container>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}
